description:
### Context
This is a Dataset for Crypto Currency called Dogecoin, Currency in INR(Indian Rs).
This dataset start from 11 Nov 2017 to 28 Jan 2022 .

### Source:
It was collected from [Yahoo Finance](https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/DOGE-INR/history?p=DOGE-INR)

### Task:
You can perform Time Series Analysis and EDA on data.
title: Dogecoin INR Dataset 2017-2022
